verbose_text: Touvier et al [XREF_BIBR] demonstrated no significant associations between TaqI and CRC, consistent with the findings of Xu et al. [XREF_BIBR] Therefore, to further investigate the correlation, in this meta-analysis, the associations between TaqI polymorphisms and CRC were assessed with updated publications to provide new insights regarding the CRC mechanism.
evidence: associations between TaqI polymorphisms and CRC
